{"tid":199061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰略大師] 燒山: 香港最少要有一個組織, 一個領袖, 去帶領香港爭取民主","createTime":"2017-04-13T02:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T08:26:53.000Z","uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54cb2dd9289da29cbb71964b82e4b8cb0f334fe9","tid":199061,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:21:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s8bYe93v6e4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds8bYe93v6e4&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5d2efe26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s8bYe93v6e4</a><br />\n<br />\n平時雖然柒, 不過今次我認同<br />\n因為香港人跟本唔撚識自己香港自己救, 冇領袖帶撚住就變撚晒做遊雲野鬼<br />\n不過個人覺得個領袖一撚定唔係品客囉"},{"pid":"8339ae7aaca7aa12bda22b172513ec967c8b2033","tid":199061,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s8bYe93v6e4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds8bYe93v6e4&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5d2efe26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s8bYe93v6e4</a><br />\n<br />\n平時雖然柒, 不過今次我認同<br />\n因為香港人跟本唔撚識自己香港自己救, 冇領袖帶撚住就變撚晒做遊雲野鬼<br />\n不過個人覺得個領袖一撚定唔係品客囉</blockquote><br />\n我認為年輕世代最有潛力喺梁天琦，論述能力強、有一定程度號召力。<br />\n<br />\n不過依加已經收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就如同流星般只閃耀一剎那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30186d9e0c0ada7c29b30bace60afeb5eb98b51c","tid":199061,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"民主黨"},{"pid":"537dd9fa928745ed8e43b1a069ffe72cb1ddeec9","tid":199061,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:36:21.000Z","msg":"ein Volk ein Reich ein F&uuml;hrer?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fe29318